features: Spacious main compartment features one large packing area, compression straps to keep contents in place and a convenient front panel opening
Expand luggage 2" for additional packing space
Keep belongings and personal information safe with integrated TSA lock and hidden ID tag
Keep contents organized with interior zippered pockets and elastic side pockets
Durable design includes corner protection and rub rails to protect against unnecessary damage
Stable navigation from a smooth telescoping handle and V-channel trolley system that retracts into a zip-away pocket when not in use
Ultra-smooth mobility attained from a custom 8 spinner wheel system
Easily lift and retrieve from luggage carousels and in transit with oversized top, side and bottom grab handles
